column5: Heres a little vid of buddy and I doing 85 mph in the Bullet. Enjoy..........
And our shoreline has never been the same Larry.  Quite the ride.

Nuts !!!! I sat on my hat too Larry, but when my Bro and I reached our destination, it was gone Didn't even see it go  And we were only doing 68mph.Had a cup of Tims in the holder beside the seat.Cup was there, don't ask me where the coffee went though
Now here's a fast boat - twin jet turbines, 150 mph. Just the sound of it warming up gives me goosebumps.
That ride even managed to put a smile on Lungelarry's face!
Nice boat, Craig. I guess I can't convince you that my 60HP tinny was the camera boat for that clip eh?
